title: Elves and Heroes
creator: Donald Alexander Mackenzie
description: LibriVox recording of Elves and Heroes, by Donald Alexander Mackenzie. Read by Matthew Reece. This volume describes, in verse, the mythical creatures and people of ancient Scotland. It also includes explanatory notes about about the characters and folk tales that inspired the author's poetry. (Introduction by Matthew Reece) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (51MB)
subject: librivox; literature; audiobook; scotland; myths; mythical creatures; verse; folk tales
